":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"條片個原理應該係:<br />\n電流會產生B field，你放舊磁石係格離就會attract or repeal(簡單版解釋<br />\n<br />\n但係點解em wave點解整唔郁指南針呢個問題，就要等其他高手解答"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"光照 磁場應該好弱 所以相對於 地球磁場 可以當illigeble <br />\n<br />\n另外 em wave 個磁場 產生嘅方向/範圍 唔同磁石<br />\n<br />\n可以睇返em wave e field 同 b field 個arrangement"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"我用太陽光照嘅話 咁夠強啦卦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地球磁場係25 to 65 microteslas<br />\n<br />\n我上網搵到嘅解釋 話原因係dc b field 同 ac b field分別<br />\nMost electromagnetic radiation is of very high frequency - the magnetic field changes many times per second. This means that the compass just doesn't have time to &quot;follow&quot; the magnetic field changes.<br />\n<br />\nThe only thing that does affect a compass is a DC magnetic field - usually this is a large piece of iron etc. that gets magnetized (e.g. by the earth's magnetic field) and thus causes distortion; or it can be a DC current loop of some kind.<br />\n<br />\nBut even the low frequencies of the mains (50 or 60 Hz depending on where you live) are much too fast to affect the compass (although in the presence of a strong source of electromagnetism, such as a large transformer, you can see vibration in the needle as observed by @vsz). Radio starts in the kHz (for long wave) to MHz (FM) or GHz (WiFi etc). And light, with wavelengths around 500 nm and a speed of 3x108 m/s, has frequencies in the hundreds of THz range. Too fast.<br />\n<br />\n原文link: <a href=\"https://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/173207/why-doesnt-light-affect-a-compass\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphysics.stackexchange.com%2Fquestions%2F173207%2Fwhy-doesnt-light-affect-a-compass&d=Pm1Q8Wns8gYR5VKS1fMOpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=519ec5d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://physics.stackexchange.com/questions/173207/why-doesnt-light-affect-a-compass</a><br />\n<br />\n都搵到條片嘅解釋 姐係inductive reactance上升 減弱左電流<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.quora.com/Why-does-brightness-of-bulb-decrease-when-an-iron-rod-is-inserted-in-a-coil&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjcofCWqqXdAhUG5bwKHd0mC2QQjjgwAHoECAQQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw0xNABwZGjceSNBXGyDPWev&amp;cshid=1536201012443\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.quora.com%2FWhy-does-brightness-of-bulb-decrease-when-an-iron-rod-is-inserted-in-a-coil%26ved%3D2ahUKEwjcofCWqqXdAhUG5bwKHd0mC2QQjjgwAHoECAQQAQ%26usg%3DAOvVaw0xNABwZGjceSNBXGyDPWev%26cshid%3D1536201012443&d=Pm1Q8Wns8gYR5VKS1fMOpL%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f2601ca2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.quora.com/Why-does-brightness-of-bulb-decrease-when-an-iron-rod-is-inserted-in-a-coil&amp;ved=2ahUKEwjcofCWqqXdAhUG5bwKHd0mC2QQjjgwAHoECAQQAQ&amp;usg=AOvVaw0xNABwZGjceSNBXGyDPWev&amp;cshid=1536201012443</a>"},{"pid":"ece3710a7629a702b31f3221cad9b53bf951e6d3","tid":806261,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f288903c4acc51d6260c5f48e83a39ae926171b","tid":806261,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f4753825363515ece6842b26a486c0e8c2769e","tid":806261,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c1eb21839bdb6322cd886b9f5b284339dac0ca5","tid":806261,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T01:40:48.000Z","msg":"條片個原理應該係:<br />\n電流會產生B field，你放舊磁石係格離就會attract or repeal(簡單版解釋<br />\n<br />\n但係點解em wave點解整唔郁指南針呢個問題，就要等其他高手解答"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"光照 磁場應該好弱 所以相對於 地球磁場 可以當illigeble <br />\n<br />\n另外 em wave 個磁場 產生嘅方向/範圍 唔同磁石<br />\n<br />\n可以睇返em wave e field 同 b field 個arrangement"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T02:37:57.000Z","msg":"我